%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (30 testers)
    participant FE as Next.js
    participant AUTH as Auth0
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as AWS RDS
    participant SE as Sentry
    participant UR as UptimeRobot

    UR->>FE: Health check (every 5 min)
    FE-->>UR: 200 OK

    U->>FE: Open datapulse.tech
    FE->>AUTH: Login redirect
    AUTH-->>FE: JWT Token
    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/analytics/summary
    API->>DB: SQL Query
    DB-->>API: Results
    API-->>FE: JSON Response
    FE-->>U: Dashboard rendered

    Note over SE: Silently watching for errors

    U->>FE: Upload Excel
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/pipeline/trigger
    API->>DB: Bronze -> Silver -> Gold
    API-->>FE: Pipeline complete

    Note over SE: If anything fails -> email alert
